  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1795177/" class="title-link">长篇政治幽默</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1795177"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/g-gb/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2103862-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/g-gb/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">大道无言</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-03-05"
      class="main-meta">2009-03-05 13:05:44</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1795177_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  哈克以为自己是一部火车头，带领着、影响着政治机器。他以为自己是至高无上的领导者。然而，一件件事实证明，不错，他是在领着那些车厢奔跑着，却是在沿着官僚机构既定的铁轨上跑着。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1795177/#comments">(1回应)</a>
